sub_title: | Passionate about Mineral resources, Volcanoes, and Education.
summary: Earth scientist fascinated by volcanoes, minerals, and natural resources; and their contribution to the energy transition for a sustainable society. I am curious towards new methods and technologies to explore and visualize the otherwise inaccessible subsurface. I enjoy data analysis and communication of discoveries towards professionals and general public.
